	<p>
		tirunaṟuṅ koṇtai-k kiḻai-p-paḷḷikku
		<lb n="2"/>k<choice><orig>i</orig><reg>ī</reg></choice>ḻ maṇṭakamu<reg>ñ</reg> caturmuka-t tiru-k-kōyiluñ ceyvittār
		<lb n="3"/><unclear>kā</unclear>viri-t-te<unclear>ṉ</unclear>-karai mirai-nāṭṭu tala-k-kuṭi vicaiya-nalluḻāṉ-ākiya
		<lb n="4"/>kumaraṉ tēvaṉ
	</p>
